msgid "Metrics"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:9
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目录"

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:11
msgid ""
"While we do not track ROS users, we do measure various aspects of the ROS "
"community to understand and track the impact of our work and identify areas "
"for improvement."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:15
msgid "Live Project Metrics"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:17
msgid ""
"`metrics.ros.org <https://metrics.ros.org>`_ is a website that hosts "
"relatively up to day visualizations of metrics about the ROS community."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:18
msgid ""
"`The Linux Foundation's LFX dashboard on ROS <https://insights."
"linuxfoundation.org/project/ros?>`_ contains an up-to-date contributor, "
"development, popularity, and project health metrics."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Our OSU OSL AWStats dashboard <https://awstats.osuosl.org/reports/packages."
"ros.org/2026/01/awstats.packages.ros.org.html>`_ provides real time data on "
"ROS package downloads."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:21
msgid ""
"*Note that you will need to specify the current month and year in the "
"AWStats URL to get the latest information.*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:23
msgid ""
"Github mains a complete list of packages and projects tagged with `#ROS "
"<https://github.com/topics/ros>`_ and `#ROS2 <https://github.com/topics/"
"ros2>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:24
msgid ""
"An up to date list of citations for the original `ROS paper <https://scholar."
"google.com/scholar?cites=1227661396257612398&as_sdt=2005&sciodt=0,5&hl=en>`_ "
"(`Quigley et al., 2009 <http://lars.mec.ua.pt/public/LAR%20Projects/"
"BinPicking/2016_RodrigoSalgueiro/LIB/ROS/icraoss09-ROS.pdf>`_), and the "
"canonical `ROS 2 paper <https://scholar.google.com/scholar?"
"oi=bibs&hl=en&cites=1227661396257612398&as_sdt=5>`_ (`Macenski et al., 2022 "
"<https://www.science.org/doi/abs/10.1126/scirobotics.abm6074>`_) are both "
"available on Google Scholar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:27
msgid "Periodic Metrics Report"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/The-ROS2-Project/Metrics.rst:29
msgid ""
"We periodically publish a metrics report that provides a quantitative view "
"of the ROS community. We're collectively learning what to measure and how "
"and evolving as systems change. Please provide feedback! Add your "
"suggestions on how to improve these reports by posting them to `ROS "
"Discourse Site Feedback Category <http://discourse.ros.org/c/site-"
"feedback>`_."
msgstr ""

